		       News file for CCPathnames
		       =========================

Revision 0.2.0-devel.0
----------------------

* Updated packaging infrastructure.

* The package now depends on CCExceptions version 0.8.0.

* The package now depends on CCMemory version 0.1.0.

* The test suite now depends on CCTests version 0.2.0.

* Renamed "ccptn_init()" to  "ccptn_library_init()".

* Changed types of exception handlers for guarded constructors.


Revision 0.1.0-beta.0
----------------------

* Initial release.


